"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-rugby-2024-0621-1456021-orchard-from-pregnancy-to-fulfilling-the-olympic-dream\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Neil Treacy RT\\u00c9 Sport Journalist Call it a hunch, but Ashleigh Orchard might well be the only athlete at this summer's Olympic Games who has thought about attempting a 'Couch to 5k' in the last year.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 22, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999789533833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hunch\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 48}, {\"ngram\": \"Ashleigh Orchard\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 70}, {\"ngram\": \"the only athlete\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 101}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Olympic Games\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 132}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'Couch\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 174}, {\"ngram\": \"5k\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 180}, {\"ngram\": \"the last year\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Orchard (n\\u00e9e Baxter) gave birth to a baby girl, Arabella, in August of last year, playing rugby at Paris 2024 could not have been further from her mind.\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabella\", \"score\": 0.9999462906543467, \"rank\": 5.371222214433702e-05, \"text\": \"Arabella\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabella\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orchard\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 215}, {\"ngram\": \"(n\\u00e9e Baxter\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 227}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 239}, {\"ngram\": \"a baby girl\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 275}, {\"ngram\": \"last year\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 288}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 303}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"her mind\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rough plan at the time was to run a marathon, and a 'Couch to 5k' programme would be the best way to get back moving.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rough plan\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"a marathon\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"Couch\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"5k' programme\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"the best way\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or so she thought.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, how did the new mother end up preparing to fulfil a lifetime ambition of becoming an Olympian?\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999022293, \"rank\": 9.797311160753663e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the new mother\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifetime ambition\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A former Ireland XVs international at wing and then flanker, Orchard was part of the Six Nations Grand Slam side of 2013, while she also featured on their famous run to the World Cup semi-finals in France the following year, before turning to Sevens where she was a regular for Ireland up until a persistent calf injury forced her to step away in 2018.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999938049768, \"rank\": 6.194994636674245e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wing\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"Orchard\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"the Six Nations Grand Slam side\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"their famous run\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Cup semi\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"Sevens\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"Ireland\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 889}, {\"ngram\": \"a persistent calf injury\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The door had always been left open to return to the Sevens programme, and after eventually getting her injury problems sorted, she returned to a development group late in 2022, playing tournaments in Elche and Dubai that led to a contract offer from David Nucifora.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elche_CF\", \"score\": 0.9999997379486901, \"rank\": 2.620515996343405e-07, \"text\": \"Elche\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elche_CF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elche_CF\"}, {\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.024781589956775e-14, \"text\": \"Dubai\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\"}, {\"begin\": 1208, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Nucifora\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Nucifora\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Nucifora\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Nucifora\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The door\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sevens programme\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"her injury problems\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"a development group\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"tournaments\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"a contract offer\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orchard got that call from Irish Rugby performance director in December 2022.\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.831071042730497, \"rank\": 0.20325868337922007, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orchard\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"that call\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later that evening found out she was, in fact, pregnant.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that evening\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had to go back to David to let him know I could not take the contract,\\\" the 33-year-old says of that fateful day.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"David\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"the contract\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"that fateful day\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I suppose at that point, I was like, 'ah this is a new adventure, I am not going back, I am not going to an Olympics'.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"a new adventure\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had Arabella obviously, and I did not think I was going to go back.\\\"\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabella\", \"score\": 0.9999462906543467, \"rank\": 5.371222214433702e-05, \"text\": \"Arabella\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabella\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than being the end of her Olympic dream, it was only the beginning, with head coach Allan Temple-Jones getting in touch to see if she still fancied a crack at making the squad for Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1037743322532693e-20, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic dream\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"only the beginning\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"head coach Allan Temple-Jones\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"touch\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"a crack\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"the squad\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her arm did not take much twisting.\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her arm\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"much twisting\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I just thought, do you know what, I am going to give this everything I have, and I will take it out of my hands, and it's in the coach's hands and if it happens, it happens, and if it does not, it does not.\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"my hands\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"the coach's hands\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just did not want to have a regret.\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a regret\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I went for it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Orchard was back in the IRFU high performance facility in Dublin in February, before her comeback on the HSBC SVNS Series in Singapore in May, where she was joined by Arabella and husband Jonathan.\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2209, \"end\": 2213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Rugby_Football_Union\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3879664164053452e-46, \"text\": \"IRFU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Rugby_Football_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Rugby_Football_Union\"}, {\"begin\": 2243, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9999040141805172, \"rank\": 9.599501654152808e-05, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}, {\"begin\": 2310, \"end\": 2319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9969616084226377, \"rank\": 0.0030475931500815847, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 2352, \"end\": 2360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabella\", \"score\": 0.9999462906543467, \"rank\": 5.371222214433702e-05, \"text\": \"Arabella\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabella\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orchard\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"her comeback\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"the HSBC SVNS Series\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"husband Jonathan\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last week, the reality hit when she got the official word that she had made the 12-player squad for next month's Olympics.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reality\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"the official word\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"the 12-player squad\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"next month's Olympics\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I kind of had this picture in my head of how I was going to react either way, but it did not happen like that,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this picture\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2535}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I started shaking, and I did not cry or anything, but I was just sitting on my chair shaking whenever he [Temple-Jones] told me.\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"my chair\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2725}, {\"ngram\": \"whenever he\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"Temple-Jones\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I was younger, I was obsessed with the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really was obsessed, that's all I wanted to do.\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I used to swim so in my head I was like, 'I want to swim in the Olympics', but I was too short and had tiny feet.\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2904}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2948}, {\"ngram\": \"tiny feet\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So this is kind of this complete bonus.\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kind of this complete bonus\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like honestly, I just want to get there.\\\"\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ulster woman's Olympic dream reached a peak as a 12-year-old, watching the Athens games in 2004.\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3079, \"end\": 3085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulster_Rugby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.781934478214723e-15, \"text\": \"Ulster\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulster_Rugby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulster_Rugby\"}, {\"begin\": 3154, \"end\": 3160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999541584623491, \"rank\": 4.584363911049226e-05, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a peak\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My biggest Olympic memory in my head is when Kelly Holmes won the 800m and 1500m,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3223, \"end\": 3235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My biggest Olympic memory\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3203}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3214}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"1500m\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I became obsessed with her.\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I made a website about her.\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a website\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can see the picture that was taken of her crossing the line of the 800m.\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3413, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the picture\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3360}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3400}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m.\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know why, that's just the one thing that sticks out for me from an Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the one thing\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3458}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While she returned to the Sevens programme in February, Orchard has not taken up the offer of a contract from the IRFU, explaining that she's still on maternity leave from her day job at Citibank which ends, coincidentally, on the Monday after they return from the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3616, \"end\": 3620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Rugby_Football_Union\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3879664164053452e-46, \"text\": \"IRFU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Rugby_Football_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Rugby_Football_Union\"}, {\"begin\": 3689, \"end\": 3697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citibank\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.325155368392774e-19, \"text\": \"Citibank\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citibank\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citibank\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Sevens programme\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3544}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3556}, {\"ngram\": \"Orchard\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"the offer\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3592}, {\"ngram\": \"a contract\", \"from\": 3596, \"to\": 3606}, {\"ngram\": \"maternity leave\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3668}, {\"ngram\": \"her day job\", \"from\": 3674, \"to\": 3685}, {\"ngram\": \"the Monday\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3739}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As she explains, balancing the physical demands of training and the private demands of being a parent is quite the juggling act.\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the physical demands\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3825}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3837}, {\"ngram\": \"the private demands\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3861}, {\"ngram\": \"a parent\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3879}, {\"ngram\": \"quite the juggling act\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the speed of the game,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 3947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the speed\", \"from\": 3914, \"to\": 3923}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not remember if it was training sessions or games, I remember turning around to one of the girls and being like, I just feel like everything is moving so fast in front of me that it's just taking my brain too long to react to it.\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 4185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sessions\", \"from\": 3988, \"to\": 3996}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 4000, \"to\": 4005}, {\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 4043, \"to\": 4052}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4096}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 4118, \"to\": 4123}, {\"ngram\": \"my brain\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am on maternity leave and I am on maternity leave for a year to be there for her [Arabella].\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"maternity leave\", \"from\": 4196, \"to\": 4211}, {\"ngram\": \"maternity leave\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4239}, {\"ngram\": \"a year\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4250}, {\"ngram\": \"her [Arabella\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I did not want to come down here and leave her at home.\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am still feeding her.\", \"from\": 4343, \"to\": 4367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not want to stop that just so I can do this.\", \"from\": 4368, \"to\": 4418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I very much wanted to put her first and the fact that the IRFU and management team all bought into that as well [is great].\", \"from\": 4419, \"to\": 4542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4477, \"end\": 4481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Rugby_Football_Union\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3879664164053452e-46, \"text\": \"IRFU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Rugby_Football_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Rugby_Football_Union\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They were like, 'bring her down, we will put you, Johnny and Arabella up [in a hotel] when we need to be down here, and the same when we are away'.\", \"from\": 4544, \"to\": 4692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hotel\", \"from\": 4622, \"to\": 4629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a mum, it's hard to just leave your child.\", \"from\": 4694, \"to\": 4740, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mum\", \"from\": 4698, \"to\": 4703}, {\"ngram\": \"your child\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I was going away for two weeks and I had to leave her, I was kind of like, I am not going to go then.\", \"from\": 4741, \"to\": 4845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two weeks\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's me and her, or it's not either of us.\\\"\", \"from\": 4846, \"to\": 4892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4888, \"to\": 4890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The support system has improved dramatically in recent years, with maternity leave in place for contracted players, while at last month's world series event in Singapore, Arabella and Orchard's husband Jonathan had a room to themselves at the team hotel.\", \"from\": 4894, \"to\": 5148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5054, \"end\": 5063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9969616084226377, \"rank\": 0.0030475931500815847, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 5065, \"end\": 5073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabella\", \"score\": 0.9999462906543467, \"rank\": 5.3712222